headline: GTA Online
subtitle: Gunrunning Spotlight with Doubled Research Speeds and 50% Off Bunker Supplies
content:
This week all Bunker Research speeds are doubled for aspiring weapons traffickers, meaning your Bunker staff will take half as much time as usual to complete research projects like weapons and vehicle mods. Plus, there’s 50% off Bunker Supplies.

Players can head to the Internet option on their mobile phone, select the ‘Money and Services’ tab and buy a Bunker through the Maze Bank Foreclosures site.
